window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A German hit man has targeted a world leader for execution. In a high octane race against the clock, an unlikely alliance must track and stop the assassin before he can carry out his unthinkable scheme. </p> <p>The fifth of the bestselling Assassin novels, <i>Blood of the Assassin</i> can be heard as a stand-alone audiobook or as the continuation of the series. </p>"; 
